    { "section": "Verse 3", "jp": "<ruby>胸<rt>むね</rt></ruby>を<ruby>締<rt>し</rt></ruby>め<ruby>付<rt>つ</rt></ruby>けられるのは<ruby>涙<rt>なみだ</rt></ruby>が<ruby>溢<rt>あふ</rt></ruby>れ<ruby>落<rt>お</rt></ruby>ちてしまうのは", "en": "The reason my chest tightens, the reason tears spill and fall", "grammar": ["passive", "te-shimau"], "tokens": [ { "surface": "胸", "lemma": "胸", "reading": "むね", "pos": "NOUN", "jlpt": "N3", "gloss": "chest" }, { "surface": "締め付けられる", "lemma": "締め付ける", "reading": "しめつけられる", "pos": "VERB", "jlpt": "N1", "gloss": "to tighten; constrict" }, { "surface": "涙", "lemma": "涙", "reading": "なみだ", "pos": "NOUN", "jlpt": "N3", "gloss": "tears" }, { "surface": "溢れ落ちて", "lemma": "溢れ落ちる", "reading": "あふれおちて", "pos": "VERB", "jlpt": "N1", "gloss": "to overflow and fall" } ] },
    { "jp": "<ruby>心<rt>こころ</rt></ruby>にもない<ruby>事<rt>こと</rt></ruby>ばかり<ruby>並<rt>なら</rt></ruby>べてしまうからか？そうなのか？", "en": "Is it because I keep lining up things I don't even mean? Is that it?", "grammar": ["te-shimau", "kara-reason"], "tokens": [ { "surface": "心にもない", "lemma": "心にもない", "reading": "こころにもない", "pos": "ADJ", "jlpt": "N1", "gloss": "insincere; not from the heart" }, { "surface": "事", "lemma": "事", "reading": "こと", "pos": "NOUN", "jlpt": "N5", "gloss": "thing; matter" }, { "surface": "並べて", "lemma": "並べる", "reading": "ならべて", "pos": "VERB", "jlpt": "N5", "gloss": "to line up; list" } ] },
